      "text": "よーし、みんなも寝静まったことだし\n遙子、一人でちょこっと晩酌しちゃうわよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "よーし、みんなも寝静まったことだし\n遙子、一人でちょこっと晩酌しちゃうわよ～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5266.666587199999,
          "startTime": 8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "……えっ！　すずちゃん、どうしたの？\nまだ寝てなかったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……えっ！　すずちゃん、どうしたの？\nまだ寝てなかったの？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.0666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "実は……誕生日パーティーが楽しかったせいか\nまだまだ眠くありませんの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "実は……誕生日パーティーが楽しかったせいか\nまだまだ眠くありませんの……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そう……じゃあ、紅茶でも淹れてあげるわね\nあと、残ったケーキも食べちゃいましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そう……じゃあ、紅茶でも淹れてあげるわね\nあと、残ったケーキも食べちゃいましょうか",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "いいんですの！？　でも、こんな夜中に食べたら\nきっと沙季に怒られますわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "いいんですの！？　でも、こんな夜中に食べたら\nきっと沙季に怒られますわ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "いいのいいの。お誕生日なんだし沙季ちゃんはもう\n寝ちゃったし……二人だけの秘密にしましょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "いいのいいの。お誕生日なんだし沙季ちゃんはもう\n寝ちゃったし……二人だけの秘密にしましょ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、これから二人でお誕生日後夜祭ね！\n私もお酒飲んじゃうわよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "それじゃあ、これから二人でお誕生日後夜祭ね！\n私もお酒飲んじゃうわよ～！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.5999974568,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_plasticbag-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9433.33587650001,
          "startTime": 67.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "誕生日に夜更かしなんてなんだかワクワクしますわね\n葵にもらったポテトチップスも開けましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "誕生日に夜更かしなんてなんだかワクワクしますわね\n葵にもらったポテトチップスも開けましょう！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、あんまり騒ぎ過ぎて\nみんなを起こさないようにしないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ふふ、あんまり騒ぎ過ぎて\nみんなを起こさないようにしないとね",
        "id": ""
      },
